              " (extract-fr) part 13 of  about: distinct species, same species, south america, such cases, thousand years, struggle for existence, struggle for life, beasts of prey, eggs or seeds

@sen615    In such cases, and endless others could be given, no one supposes that the fertility of the animals or plants has been suddenly and temporarily increased in any sensible degree.

