              " (extract-fr) part 50 of  about: natural selection

@sen2260    I repeated these observations on some other species of Oxalis with the same result; in some of them the movement was distinct, but was best seen in the young leaves; in others it was extremely slight.

              " (extract-fr) part 50 of  about: natural selection

